OL,7,FLess than a year ago, Dr Vlad Beliavsky
OL,8,Fwas wondering how to celebrate the
OL,9,Fcompletion of his first book. Exhausted
OL,10,Fby all his writing but feeling proud,
OL,11,Fhe had returned home to Ukraine after
OL,12,Ffour years of working in the UK and
OL,13,Fplanned to go travelling for a few
OL,14,Fmonths before his next project. Top of
OL,15,Fhis agenda: surfing and cycling in
OL,16,FAsia, with plenty of relaxing
OL,17,Fbreakfasts and coffee by the ocean.
OL,19,FThen the Russian invasion began.
